                The Vulindlela CAPRISA Research Clinic adjoins 
                the Mafakatini Primary Health Care Clinic in the
                rural Vulindlela district in KwaZulu-Natal. The
                research facility, which hosts an adolescent-friendly
                clinic, has a close working relationship with the
                local community to study new approaches to HIV 
                prevention and treatment.

                

            </p>
